      <section eId="sec_473">
        <num>473</num>
        <heading>Savings clause</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_473__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>any motor\nvehicles sold by such person are limited to used motor vehicles that\nhave been previously used exclusively and regularly by such person in\nthe conduct of business and used motor vehicles traded in on motor\nvehicles sold by such person,</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_473__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>warranty repairs performed by such\nperson on motor vehicles are limited to those motor vehicles that it\nowns, previously owned or takes in trade, and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_473__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>motor vehicle\nfinancing provided by such person to retail consumers for motor vehicles\nis limited to vehicles sold by such person in the conduct of business;\nor\n  2. The direct or indirect ownership, affiliation or control of a\nperson described in subdivision one of this section.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
